## User Validation

**Every button/select/modal handler MUST validate:**

```typescript
// BEFORE processing
const character = await getCharacterByUserId(interaction.user.id);
if (character.id !== targetId) {
  return interaction.reply({
    content: "Đây không phải nhân vật của ngươi.",
    flags: MessageFlags.Ephemeral,
  });
}
```

**Never process a button click from a non-owner.**
**Never assume `interaction.user.id` matches the character.**
**Validate, then process.**

