## Embed Design

### Color Guide

| Category | Hex Color | Decimal |
|----------|-----------|---------|
| Cultivation | Purple | 0x9966ff |
| Breakthrough | Gold | 0xffcc00 |
| Alchemy | Orange | 0xff6600 |
| Sect | Blue | 0x00ccff |
| Combat | Red | 0xff3333 |
| Encounter | Teal | 0x66ffcc |
| Success | Green | 0x00ff00 |
| Error | Red | 0xff0000 |
| Warning | Amber | 0xffaa00 |
| Info | Light Blue | 0x0099ff |
| Neutral | Gray | 0x888888 |

### Embed Rules

1. **Max 25 fields** — Discord limit.
2. **Title under 256 characters.**
3. **Description under 4096 characters.**
4. **Footer for attribution** — Always include `Thiên Nam Võ Lục`.
5. **Timestamp for temporal events** — Use for log entries.
6. **Thumbnail for character profile** — If user has avatar.

### Embed Template

```typescript
new EmbedBuilder()
  .setTitle(`[Emoji] [Title]`)
  .setColor(EmbedColors.[Category])
  .setDescription(`[Brief description]`)
  .addFields([
    { name: "[Label]", value: "[Value]", inline: true },
    { name: "[Label]", value: "[Value]", inline: true },
  ])
  .setFooter({ text: "Thiên Nam Võ Lục" })
  .setTimestamp();
```

